{
  "stem": "23579.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He risked his life, and he went to the police.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, the police was [INAUDIBLE], the head of the police of Novogrudok.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, [INAUDIBLE], I will do everything for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, you have to take out the lady with the two daughters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he took her out before an hour to finish the whole ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, my husband's two brothers were in there, in the police for dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know because I didn't know my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know my husband.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know the brothers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But his mother, she was coming to the ghetto, asks if somebody can do something for them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were some people, they were asking her $100 in gold.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My husband was telling me about this later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they didn't have the gold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they went where all the Jews went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In this time, my father took it out, the woman and the two children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're writing now a book.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] writing a book about this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, a Jew is a big [NON-ENGLISH], a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He has always a watch, a ring, a pair of shoes, a pair of boots.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were changing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they were on the market and working, the paisanos, they were coming and said, I need a watch.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I will give you the food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they gave to him the watch, the paisano, and he will bring them bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the peasants.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the only way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They couldn't buy it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] no food in places to buy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were bringing them for the morning, for a ring, for boots, for everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's what.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was a hunger, too, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A lot of hunger.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
